    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund full sick pay for employees that are off work due to COVID",
        "additional_details": "People work hard to earn enough money to covers their bills, and many have no chance to save, so having to self-isolate for 2 weeks will have a devastating financial effect on many families and households. People cannot afford not to work. They would safely stay at home if they could afford to.",
        "background": "Families cannot afford to have 2 weeks off work, due to Track & Trace if employers will only pay employees SSP (\u00a395.85 per week). The Government should help employers pay their staff their full wage. This could operate in a similar way to the furlough scheme.",
